comments: Kanter (BOS) establishes a legal screening position in Richardson's (PHI) path and absorbs the contact.
As Hayward (BOS) gathers the ball incidental foot to foot contact occurs with Embiid (PHI).

Brown (BOS) briefly grasps Richardson's (PHI) arm during the hand-off but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Kanter (BOS) makes some contact with Embiid's (PHI) body in the post but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Tatum (BOS).
Simmons (PHI) engages with Tatum (BOS) during the screen but does not affect his FOM.
Kanter (BOS) makes contact with Richardson (PHI) during the screen and the contact dislodges him from his obtain position.
Kanter (BOS) makes marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) during the screen that does not prevent him to defend through the play.
Kanter (BOS) establishes legal position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and firms up on his shoulder but contact does not prevent him to defend through the play.
Hayward (BOS) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Richardson (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Brown (BOS) during his drive.
Kanter (BOS) makes some contact with Simmons' (PHI) during the screen but contact does not affect his ability to defend through the play.
Simmons (PHI) places his hand to Walker's (CHA) front but the contact is marginal.

Richardson (PHI) clamps Browns' (BOS) arm while the ball in being thrown in and affects his ability to receive the pass.
